122
00:11:13,340 --> 00:11:17,177
No worries. Thanks again for the cookies.

123
00:11:17,261 --> 00:11:18,762
I'll bring by more!

124
00:11:20,097 --> 00:11:21,139
Please.

125
00:11:55,299 --> 00:11:57,301
-Mr. Scout, how are you doing?
-Hey, Judd.

126
00:12:38,008 --> 00:12:41,595
