128
00:12:42,763 --> 00:12:45,766
-Yesterday. You were gone.
-I was?

129
00:12:45,849 --> 00:12:49,645
Oh, yeah. Dylan took over training
in your stead to great success.

130
00:12:49,728 --> 00:12:53,106
